<h4 style-"color:black">Yeplive™ is built for discovery.</h4>
<p> Find out what's happening inside that concert hall you hear cheering from, stumble upon your favorite artist streaming from an event in your neighborhood, or be part of a political event from the vantage point of the front lines, all with the click of a pin!</p> 

<p>Livestream a video with the click of a record button, engage with your viewers, and share socially — it's that easy. For livestreams where location isn't vital, you can also search Yeplive™ by tag or title. Yeplive™ is a new way to see and connect with your world. Experience cool moments as they unfold, and share to multiple social media platforms like Facebook, Twitter, and more. Yeplive™ is where you go to be the first to know. Get front row seats to the things that matter to you, from entertainment and sports to philanthropy and political events. Live in the know™.</p>

<h4 style="color:black;">The founders of Yeplive™ are catalysts for social good.</h4>
<p> We want to see massive global shifts in this lifetime, and live by the motto #bethechange.</p>
In addition to being a platform that showcases the social sharing of entertainment, sports, and life, Yeplive™ brings awareness to causes that need our attention.<p>

<h4 style="color:black;">How better to feel connected to someone in the world than to see things from their perspective?</h4>
<p>Yeplive™ is the voice of people. Distance may separate us, but Yeplive™ brings us closer. From everyday happenings with friends and family, to checking out concerts and nightclubs live, to world news and beautiful moments, Yeplive™ is here to live in the moment with you. Everyone has a story to tell and we want to hear it. Welcome to the storybook of our world.</p>

<p><em>We'd love to hear from you. Reach out to us socially, or drop us a line at info@yeplive.com.</em></p>
